{"tid":1973682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬道立：從未感受到中共干預香港司法獨立","createTime":"2020-04-15T10:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T10:30:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8a27b7098df81b74f129b71c1cb8c8e1972c16","tid":1973682,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:26:35.000Z","msg":"終審法院首席法官馬道立今日（15日）發聲明，回應路透社昨日（14日）報道，他表示自2010年擔任終院首席法官以來，終院首席法官從未在任何時間遇到或感受到內地機關以任何形式就香港司法獨立，包括委任法官的事宜，作出干預；司法獨立受《基本法》保障，是香港法治的重要一環。<br />\n<br />\n路透社昨報道，有接近馬道立的人說，馬道立要抗衡共產黨官員視法治為最終須維護一黨統治的工具（the rule of law ultimately must be a tool to preserve one-party rule），又指出雖然馬道立不是被迫離開，但持續捍衛法院之戰令他日漸沮喪。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥早前宣布，任命終院常任法官張舉能為終院首席法官，將待立法會同意後，根據《基本法》第88條作出任命，任命2021年1月11日生效，接替現任終院首席法官馬道立。"},{"pid":"727f134bd838e3a2e7a143f86ba846f6c243eddb","tid":1973682,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200415/s00001/1586945552254/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200415%2Fs00001%2F1586945552254%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=641233e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200415%2Fs00001%2F1586945552254%2F&h=bf6bd534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200415/s00001/1586945552254/</a>"},{"pid":"f97b02c3e240c0dd0cf5f55998e707fd3c2468af","tid":1973682,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxa8D5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsxa8D5A.jpg&h=14d9e7a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1537fa6e6d12f4861757b3c34dd27bfc5bd5580f","tid":1973682,"uid":178290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:28:08.000Z","msg":"一國兩制好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n退休就快啦"},{"pid":"bd2f3dd884b079316972d2940a0cd5a9f180367d","tid":1973682,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"法治zombie?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655ba180e64c8d7b84762f9b85e7a0ea724d075e","tid":1973682,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"釋法已經係啦"},{"pid":"68763659e24bb67dcef090ec42175ce08b4fca49","tid":1973682,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/200111_CR_%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F200111_CR_%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2587.jpg&h=613b0320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">巴打識玩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}